cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.MM, cs.CR 

This paper deals with the spectrum allocation problem in heterogeneous networks, which is a topic related to network infrastructure and communication systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves optimization techniques and information theory, which are related to cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also discusses simulation results, which may fall under cs.MM (Multimedia) or cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
